'''比利·奧古斯特'''（{{lang-da|Bille August}}；{{bd|1948年|11月9日}}）是[[丹麥|丹麥]]電影導演，他曾獲得兩屆-{zh-cn:[[戛纳电影节|法国戛纳电影节]];zh-tw:[[坎城影展|法國坎城影展]];zh-hk:[[康城影展|法國康城影展]];zh-sg:[[戛纳电影节|法国戛纳电影节]];zh-mo:[[康城影展|法國康城影展]];}-[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]（《[[比利小英雄|比利小英雄]]》與《{{link-sv|善意的背叛|Den goda viljan}}》）、一屆[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|奧斯卡最佳外語片獎]]（《[[比利小英雄|比利小英雄]]》）、一屆[[金球獎最佳外語片|金球獎最佳外語片]]（《[[比利小英雄|比利小英雄]]》）。<ref name="cannes-1988.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/299/year/1988.html |title=Festival de Cannes: Pelle the Conqueror |accessdate=27 July 2009 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2011-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910205700/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/299/year/1988.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cannes-1992.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/12/year/1992.html |title=Festival de Cannes: The Best Intentions |accessdate=14 August 2009 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2014-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215012949/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/12/year/1992.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/film/pelle-conqueror |title=Winners & Nominees - Pelle The Conqueror |accessdate=8 September 2009 |work=goldenglobes.com |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129144032/https://www.goldenglobes.com/film/pelle-conqueror |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/Search/GetResults?query=%7B%22AwardCategoryExactId%22:27,%22IsHyperlinkQuery%22:true,%22AwardShowFrom%22:61,%22Sort%22:%223-Award%20Category-Chron%22,%22Search%22:%22Basic%22%7D |title=1988 (61st) FOREIGN LANGUAGE FILM |accessdate=8 September 2009 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815104104/http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/Search/GetResults?query=%7B%22AwardCategoryExactId%22:27,%22IsHyperlinkQuery%22:true,%22AwardShowFrom%2